ment/analyzer system. Material classification should be null for instruments. Brand 'Merilyzer' is missing from current data. Conflict exists between generic family-level naming and model-specific technical specifications in brochure. Recommend rename to include 'Merilyzer' brand and clarify whether this page represents the entire family or a specific model (likely CelQuant 5 Plus based on 5-part differential spec). Review required to determine proper page structure: single family page vs. individual model pages.","proposed_recommended_action":"rename","proposed_semantic_anatomy_scope":["Blood/Hematologic System"],"proposed_semantic_brand_system":"Merilyzer CelQuant","proposed_semantic_coating_default":null,"proposed_semantic_confidence":0.85,"proposed_semantic_family_group":"Merilyzer CelQuant Hematology Analyzer Family","proposed_semantic_implant_class":"N/A - Diagnostic Instrument","proposed_semantic_material_default":null,"proposed_semantic_parent_brand":"Merilyzer","proposed_semantic_procedure_scope":["Complete Blood Count (CBC)","Differential Blood Analysis","Leukocyte Classification","Platelet Counting","Blood Cell Morphology Assessment"],"proposed_semantic_review_required":true,"proposed_semantic_system_type":"Hematology Analyzer Platform","proposed_semantic_use_case_tags":["Clinical Laboratory","Hematology","CBC Testing","Differential Analysis","Blood Cell Counting","Flow Cytometry"],"proposed_web_verification_status":"review_required_ambiguity"}}]
